atic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/ffe33d1058865cb213e2cbd7f43166c4.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It's not just a random car, it's a rally car</strong></h2>You are dealing with a rally car - a purpose-built machine. Turbos, coilovers, proper tires and performance transmissions will sooner or later be installed in your vehicle. The car has a lot of extra features that you need to keep an eye on. Make it as good as possible and earn fans and money as a part of a champion rally team.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/c65f58a6aa0add13d05be0bb968bef04.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/c65f58a6aa0add13d05be0bb968bef04.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic rally car models with lots of interaction<br></li><li>Possibility to work on the electronics of your cars<br></li><li>Car damage and cleaning systems<br></li><li>Ability to paint your cars<br></li><li>Equipped field workshop to make repairs<br></li><li>Extensive economic system<br></li><li>Advanced vehicle development system<br></li><li>Realistic graphics<br></li><li>Advanced car appearance personalization system<br></li><li>Timed repair segments<br></li><li>Extensive tuning options<br></li><li>League progression system<br></li><li>Many achievements to unlock</li></ul>",
